I'm an assistant professor in the Dept. of Computer Science and Engineering. Expertise I work in the intersection of compilers & programming languages with high-performance and quantum computing. My goals are to make program execution faster and more reliable while also improving their portability across different architectures and simplifying the users' and scientists' effort to do so.
